WEBVTT

00:00.338 --> 00:01.338
<i>Sports Illustrated has this team</i>

00:01.339 --> 00:03.291
<i>as the number one high school
football team in Texas.</i>

00:03.292 --> 00:05.288
Got yourself a heck
of a quarterback.

00:05.305 --> 00:07.138
He's a good boy.
Very proud of him.

00:07.141 --> 00:08.704
Is it true, Mr. Street,
that--

00:08.717 --> 00:09.607
That I love Lyla Garrity?

00:09.673 --> 00:11.940
Here's to God and football

00:12.007 --> 00:13.673
and, ten years
from now, Street,

00:13.740 --> 00:15.940
good friends livin' large
in Texas.

00:16.008 --> 00:17.040
We feel fully prepared

00:17.100 --> 00:19.005
to represent
this beloved community

00:19.075 --> 00:20.049
this Friday night

00:20.108 --> 00:21.078
and every Friday night.

00:21.149 --> 00:23.171
You've earned this.
The right to win.

00:23.248 --> 00:24.812
<i>Street throws a wobble.</i>

00:24.827 --> 00:25.603
Picked off by Chandler.

00:26.125 --> 00:27.972
Street the only one
that can get to him.

00:28.387 --> 00:30.053
Gigantic hit on Street.

00:32.907 --> 00:34.183
A third-string quarterback.
Saracen!

00:34.188 --> 00:34.981
No one's seen
this guy play.

00:35.178 --> 00:36.231
Start throwing
the ball, son.

00:36.677 --> 00:37.422
<i>Dropping back to pass,</i>

00:37.785 --> 00:39.341
and he throws the ball--
Oh, man.

00:39.597 --> 00:40.903
Man, can this kid
throw the ball.

00:41.426 --> 00:43.543
Give all of us
the strength to remember

00:43.605 --> 00:44.570
that what we have
is special.

00:44.935 --> 00:47.000
That it can be taken
from us.

00:47.078 --> 00:48.842
And that when it is,
we will be tested.

00:51.625 --> 00:52.223
It is a blessing

00:52.226 --> 00:53.502
to be in the house
of the Lord

00:53.508 --> 00:54.560
amongst believers.

00:54.578 --> 00:55.760
Amen.

00:55.777 --> 00:57.133
We do know
that on Friday night,

00:57.135 --> 00:59.231
one of our brothers,
brother Jason,

00:59.237 --> 01:02.562
was injured
in the football game.

01:02.605 --> 01:03.602
The doctors are saying

01:03.608 --> 01:05.580
that possible
he could be paralyzed.

01:05.677 --> 01:09.001
But we know of a doctor
who's greater

01:09.078 --> 01:10.742
than any doctor.

01:10.806 --> 01:12.743
Yes, yes.

01:12.808 --> 01:17.042
I have prayed with Mitchell
and Joanne Street.

01:17.105 --> 01:19.601
And as an entire
community,

01:19.677 --> 01:23.801
we have come together
in prayer and hope.

01:23.876 --> 01:26.542
And faith

01:26.608 --> 01:29.243
And with these prayers,
this faith,

01:29.308 --> 01:32.403
this hope,
I believe Jason Street

01:33.667 --> 01:36.243
will once again walk in
on his own two feet

01:37.497 --> 01:39.691
and join
this congregation

01:39.766 --> 01:41.990
and rejoice with us.

01:42.068 --> 01:44.632
I saw that tackle,
little brother.

01:44.697 --> 01:47.661
I saw him hit that turf.

01:47.735 --> 01:50.063
Tell you what I think.

01:50.138 --> 01:53.163
He's talking about wanting
to play football.

01:53.236 --> 01:54.762
He ain't ever
gonna walk again.

01:56.836 --> 01:58.362
And we know
he's gonna be fine.

01:58.436 --> 01:59.331
He's gonna walk again.

02:00.837 --> 02:03.260
We're prayin' for him.

02:09.294 --> 02:11.061
Best case scenario,
Jason's probably out

02:11.136 --> 02:12.462
for a month.

02:12.538 --> 02:14.430
You know, it's probably
a lot longer than that.

02:15.568 --> 02:19.260
But, uh, we need a plan
for Friday night.

02:19.336 --> 02:20.533
Heck, we--

02:20.597 --> 02:23.091
Heck, we need a--need a plan
for the rest of the season,

02:23.166 --> 02:24.591
is what we need, Eric.

02:26.528 --> 02:27.191
So tell me,

02:27.268 --> 02:31.293
you think little Matt Saracen
can get it done?

02:37.788 --> 02:39.320
I guess we're fixin'
to find out.

02:39.697 --> 02:40.460
Yep.

02:40.465 --> 02:43.003
That was a nice sermon,
wasn't it?

02:43.967 --> 02:45.061
Hey, Matt.

02:45.136 --> 02:46.862
Come here.

02:48.366 --> 02:50.802
How's it goin', Coach?

02:50.868 --> 02:53.100
We got a lotta work
to do, son.

02:54.907 --> 02:56.003
Yes sir.

