20:25.135 --> 20:28.060
You're a good man.

20:28.135 --> 20:29.762
You're a good man.

20:33.337 --> 20:35.560
You're what makes guys like me
wanna coach.

20:35.637 --> 20:39.431
You are a good man.

20:39.508 --> 20:42.001
Thank you.

20:42.067 --> 20:45.333
I'm sorry if I--

20:45.406 --> 20:48.800
